	<item>
		<title>Highway &#038; Road</title>
		<link>./../highway-road/index.html</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[geopadmin]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Mon, 06 Apr 2020 03:10:20 +0000</pubDate>
				<guid isPermaLink="false">https://themecrafter.com/kyber/?post_type=service&#038;p=709</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[At every stage of the road and highway lifecycle, we ensure that the roads are safe and stable.]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<div class="vc_row wpb_row vc_row-fluid vc_custom_1586492563322 kyber-bg-color-transparent kyber-background-position-left-top kyber-title-color-default"><div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-12 kyber-bg-color-transparent kyber-background-position-left-top kyber-title-color-default"><div class="vc_column-inner"><div class="wpb_wrapper"><h2 style="font-size: 30px;line-height: 40px;text-align: left" class="vc_custom_heading" >Highway &amp; Road</h2>
	<div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element  vc_custom_1645459528895" >
		<div class="wpb_wrapper">
			<p>At every stage of the road and highway lifecycle, we ensure that the roads are safe and stable.</p>
<p>Highway and road service maintenance is an important investment in the infrastructure of the state, city, and municipality. To achieve compliance with numerous professional standards and regulations, detailed planning and diverse technical knowledge are required.</p>
<p>The regulated road service components, such as survey, investigation, designing, construction, environment, maintenance, and safety, must be understood by government and transportation authorities, developers, and operators. Unnoticed structural damage might pose a safety risk and be costly to fix in the future.</p>
<p>Third-party road testing and inspection are included in Geoprecise road service and highway maintenance services to verify that road works constructions are safe, stable, reliable, and comply with standards. Our quality assurance services improve road structural performance, while our cost-effective refurbishing solutions extend the life of road infrastructure. We also assist with planning and provide legal assurance.</p>
<p>Our consultants assist you in maintaining single-source control over cash flow and utilization, improving planning and budgeting, and measuring project outcomes consistently. We help you finish projects on schedule and on budget, while also ensuring road user safety and reducing business, financial, and legal risks. Other advantages include:</p>

		</div>
	</div>
</div></div></div></div><div class="vc_row wpb_row vc_row-fluid vc_custom_1587041640569 kyber-bg-color-transparent kyber-background-position-left-top kyber-title-color-default"><div class="kyber-accordion-style-1 wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-12 kyber-bg-color-transparent kyber-background-position-left-top kyber-title-color-default"><div class="vc_column-inner"><div class="wpb_wrapper"><div class="vc_tta-container" data-vc-action="collapse"><div class="vc_general vc_tta vc_tta-accordion vc_tta-color-white vc_tta-style-classic vc_tta-shape-square vc_tta-o-shape-group vc_tta-controls-align-left vc_custom_1586514109796"><div class="vc_tta-panels-container"><div class="vc_tta-panels"><div class="vc_tta-panel vc_active" id="1585768153475-cb5f3c27-f8e2" data-vc-content=".vc_tta-panel-body"><div class="vc_tta-panel-heading"><h4 class="vc_tta-panel-title vc_tta-controls-icon-position-right"><a href="#1585768153475-cb5f3c27-f8e2" data-vc-accordion data-vc-container=".vc_tta-container"><span class="vc_tta-title-text">Delivering projects on time – </span><i class="vc_tta-controls-icon vc_tta-controls-icon-plus"></i></a></h4></div><div class="vc_tta-panel-body">
	<div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element " >
		<div class="wpb_wrapper">
			<p>Delivering projects on time – with single-source control, enabled by our interdisciplinary support and project management advisory.</p>

		</div>
	</div>
</div></div><div class="vc_tta-panel" id="1585768254686-8ec51f11-f577" data-vc-content=".vc_tta-panel-body"><div class="vc_tta-panel-heading"><h4 class="vc_tta-panel-title vc_tta-controls-icon-position-right"><a href="#1585768254686-8ec51f11-f577" data-vc-accordion data-vc-container=".vc_tta-container"><span class="vc_tta-title-text">Reducing costs –</span><i class="vc_tta-controls-icon vc_tta-controls-icon-plus"></i></a></h4></div><div class="vc_tta-panel-body">
	<div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element " >
		<div class="wpb_wrapper">
			<p>Reducing costs – through our expertise in identifying road maintenance repair needs and making restoration recommendations with cost efficiency in mind.</p>

		</div>
	</div>
</div></div><div class="vc_tta-panel" id="1585768253236-3404ad31-9228" data-vc-content=".vc_tta-panel-body"><div class="vc_tta-panel-heading"><h4 class="vc_tta-panel-title vc_tta-controls-icon-position-right"><a href="#1585768253236-3404ad31-9228" data-vc-accordion data-vc-container=".vc_tta-container"><span class="vc_tta-title-text">Gaining planning and legal certainty – </span><i class="vc_tta-controls-icon vc_tta-controls-icon-plus"></i></a></h4></div><div class="vc_tta-panel-body">
	<div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element " >
		<div class="wpb_wrapper">
			<p>Gaining planning and legal certainty – with our in-depth knowledge of technical directives and standards, along with best-in-class advisory on project planning, cost control, and material selection.</p>

		</div>
	</div>
</div></div><div class="vc_tta-panel" id="1585768269870-21174b1c-1030" data-vc-content=".vc_tta-panel-body"><div class="vc_tta-panel-heading"><h4 class="vc_tta-panel-title vc_tta-controls-icon-position-right"><a href="#1585768269870-21174b1c-1030" data-vc-accordion data-vc-container=".vc_tta-container"><span class="vc_tta-title-text">Ensuring the safety of road users –</span><i class="vc_tta-controls-icon vc_tta-controls-icon-plus"></i></a></h4></div><div class="vc_tta-panel-body">
	<div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element " >
		<div class="wpb_wrapper">
			<p>Ensuring the safety of road users – with our expert third-party quality assurance that optimizes the performance of your road structures, enhances traffic flow, and inspires trust in your reputation.</p>

		</div>
	</div>
</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div>
]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
